*اهورامزدا ([[File:OldPersian-AURAMAZDAAHA.svg|15px]]) 
*هېواد  ([[File:OldPersian-BUUMISH.svg|15px]] – ''búmiš'')
*خاوره ([[File:OldPersian-DAHYAAUSH-2.svg|15px]] – ''dahajauša'')
 
